data.description:
Dont miss this amazing opportunity to own a 2-family detached home with a 4-car garage!
Situated on a 4,000-square-foot lot, this property stands out for its ample space, featuring front and rear patios. Recently updated, it is a great opportunity as a primary residence or for maximizing income as an investment property! Delivered vacant. 
Upon entry, you're greeted by a welcoming patio and garden. The first unit spans two floors and includes a recently updated open kitchen, two spacious bedrooms suitable for king-size beds, and access to the rear patio. The basement serves as an extension to the first unit, offering extra living space, a kitchen, a bedroom/office, a full bathroom, and substantial storage. 
The second-floor unit comprises three bedrooms, with one bedroom easily converting to additional storage or office space. The living room features a generous, open layout that expands into a renovated kitchen with modern appliances. 
The location of this incredible property is highly convenient, with nearby bus stops, a Key Foods grocery store, and various neighborhood amenities. Additionally, the Kings Plaza shopping mall is just a 10-minute drive away!
